Class Entity

java.lang.Object
com.sangarius.oop.library.persistence.entity.Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Book, Category, Library, Loan, Review, User
public abstract class Entity extends Object
Abstract base class for entities in the library management system. Provides common functionality and properties for all entities.
